description: Architecture rules — Vertical Slice, boundaries, patterns
globs: src/**/*.{ts,tsx}

## Architecture Rules
1. core/konw about: nothing
2. shared/imports from: core/
3. features/imports from: shared/, core/
4. No feature imports another feature directly
5. Services handle data operations, stores handle state, components handle UI
6. Lazy load all route-level components
7. DbAdapter interface for storage abstraction
8. Types centralized in shared/types/index.ts
9. Config centralized in core/config/index.ts
10. One component per file
